rows.label: tev035702_MSG0001
rows.name:
I have to say, you dress really well. You might even
give Victoria a run for her fashion money, actually?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035702_MSG0002
rows.name:
I love someone who's not afraid to play with color,
you know what I mean? Maybe we Ma-non should
take a page from from your book.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035702_MSG0003
rows.name:
...You know what? I'm gonna pick your brain and
work some of of these fresh ideas into our new line.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035702_MSG0004
rows.name:
Victoria and I are going to turn the world of of
intergalactic apparel upside-down, I think? Yes!
Just you wait![ST:wait ]
